"ADRENAL PUMP"

The adrenal pump is an bioware modification to the users adrenal gland which
causes higher and more rapid onset of andrenaline rush. It can be triggered
during stressful situations or by manual intake of the drug ACTH. 

When activated it grants the user +1 Quickness, +1 Strength, +1 Willpower
and +2 Reaction.

Adrenal Pumps are not compatible with move-by-wire.
